                            How do I apply for staff?
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-item-body">
                            <div class="accordion-item-body-content">
                                If you're passionate about RT Network and want to help improve the community, you can apply for a staff position through our website <a href="requests.html" style="text-decoration:underline;font-weight:600;color:#D2D0D0;">here</a>. We are always looking for dedicated, responsible, and friendly players to join our team. To apply, simply fill out the staff application form, providing relevant details about your experience, skills, and why you'd be a great fit. Our staff team carefully reviews all applications and selects individuals who align with our values and goals. If your application is successful, you’ll be contacted for an interview, and we’ll walk you through the onboarding process.
                            </div>
