                        Is RT Network pay-to-win?
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item-body">
                        <div class="accordion-item-body-content">
                            No, RT Network is not pay-to-win. While we offer ranks, cosmetic items, and other perks to support the server, we ensure that any items that can affect the fairness of competition are obtainable for free. While donations are very much appreciated, we are committed to maintaining a balanced and enjoyable experience for everyone, regardless of whether they donate or not.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item">
