                        What do I do if I got banned?
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item-body">
                        <div class="accordion-item-body-content">
                            If you get banned, it means you've likely violated one of our server rules. However, we understand that mistakes happen, and if you believe your ban was unfair, you have the option to submit a ban appeal through our website. When submitting an appeal, make sure to include any relevant details, such as the reason for your ban and any information that may help your case. Our staff carefully reviews all ban appeals, and we will notify you of the outcome. We aim to be fair and transparent in all of our decisions, so your appeal will be taken seriously.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <div class="accordion-item-header">
                        Why should I vote for the server?
                    </div>
